query: /* Select with Simple Date Range Filter */ SELECT * FROM data WHERE time >= '2023-01-01' AND time < '2024-01-01'
original_query:
-- Select with Simple Date Range Filter 
SELECT * FROM data WHERE time >= '2023-01-01' AND time < '2024-01-01'

query: /* Select with Multiple Filters (Date Range and Category) */ SELECT * FROM data WHERE time >= '2023-01-01' AND time < '2024-01-01' AND power_output > 0
original_query:
-- Select with Multiple Filters (Date Range and Category)
SELECT * FROM data WHERE time >= '2023-01-01' AND time < '2024-01-01' AND power_output > 0

query: /* Select with ORDER BY and Limit */ SELECT * FROM data ORDER BY power_output DESC NULLS FIRST LIMIT 50
original_query:
-- Select with ORDER BY and Limit
SELECT * FROM data ORDER BY power_output DESC LIMIT 50

query: /* Get top 50 rows by power output */ /* AGGREGATE Queries */ /* Basic Aggregates */ SELECT AVG(power_output) AS avg_power_output, MAX(power_output) AS max_power_output, MIN(power_output) AS min_power_output FROM data
original_query:
-- Get top 50 rows by power output

-- AGGREGATE Queries 
-- Basic Aggregates
SELECT AVG(power_output) as avg_power_output, MAX(power_output) as max_power_output, MIN(power_output) as min_power_output FROM data

query: /* Aggregates with Date Range Filter (Corrected: use AND, standard date format) */ SELECT AVG(power_output) AS avg_power_output, MAX(power_output) AS max_power_output, MIN(power_output) AS min_power_output FROM data WHERE time >= '2023-01-01' AND time < '2024-01-01'
original_query:
-- Aggregates with Date Range Filter (Corrected: use AND, standard date format)
SELECT AVG(power_output) as avg_power_output, MAX(power_output) as max_power_output, MIN(power_output) as min_power_output FROM data WHERE time >= '2023-01-01' AND time < '2024-01-01'

query: /* Aggregates Grouped by Year with Ordering */ SELECT EXTRACT(YEAR FROM time) AS year, AVG(power_output) AS avg_power_output, MAX(power_output) AS max_power_output, MIN(power_output) AS min_power_output FROM data WHERE time >= '2023-01-01' AND time < '2024-01-01' GROUP BY EXTRACT(YEAR FROM time) ORDER BY EXTRACT(YEAR FROM time)
original_query:
-- Aggregates Grouped by Year with Ordering
SELECT
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM time) as year,
    AVG(power_output) as avg_power_output,
    MAX(power_output) as max_power_output,
    MIN(power_output) as min_power_output
FROM data
WHERE time >= '2023-01-01' AND time < '2024-01-01'
GROUP BY EXTRACT(YEAR FROM time)
ORDER BY EXTRACT(YEAR FROM time)

query: /* JOIN Queries */ /* Simple Self-Join to Calculate Power Change */ SELECT t1.time, t1.power_output AS power_output, t2.power_output AS previous_power, t1.power_output - t2.power_output AS power_change FROM data AS t1 JOIN data AS t2 ON t1.time = t2.time
original_query:
-- JOIN Queries
-- Simple Self-Join to Calculate Power Change
SELECT
    t1.time,     
    t1.power_output as power_output,  
    t2.power_output as previous_power, 
    t1.power_output - t2.power_output as power_change
FROM data t1
JOIN data t2 ON t1.time = t2.time

query: /* WINDOW FUNCTION Queries */ /* Running total */ SELECT time, power_output AS power_output, SUM(power_output) OVER (ORDER BY time) AS running_total FROM data ORDER BY time
original_query:
-- WINDOW FUNCTION Queries
-- Running total
SELECT
    time,
    power_output as power_output,
    SUM(power_output) OVER (ORDER BY time) as running_total
FROM data
ORDER BY time

query: /* Power output changes */ SELECT d1.time, d1.power_output, d2.power_output AS previous_power_output, d1.power_output - d2.power_output AS power_change FROM data AS d1 LEFT JOIN data AS d2 ON d2.time = (SELECT MAX(time) FROM data WHERE time < d1.time) ORDER BY d1.time
original_query:
-- Power output changes
SELECT
    d1.time,
    d1.power_output,
    d2.power_output AS previous_power_output,
    d1.power_output - d2.power_output AS power_change
FROM data d1
LEFT JOIN data d2 ON d2.time = (SELECT MAX(time) FROM data WHERE time < d1.time)
ORDER BY d1.time
